quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  21,58,"Nuko byose arabijanjagura asiga ikinini muri byo, kugira ngo (nibagaruka) bakibaza (uwagiriye nabi imana zabo)"
  21,59,"(Bagarutse babona imana zabo zamenaguritse) baravuga bati \"Ni nde wagize atyaimana zacu?Mu by’ukuri, ni umwe mu bagizi ba nabi"
  21,60,"Baravuga bati \"Twumvise umusore uzivuga nabi witwa Ibrahimu"
  21,61,"Baravuga bati \"Nimumuzane imbere y’abantu kugira ngo birebere (ibyo agiye gukorerwa)"
  21,62,"Baravuga bati \"Ese yewe Ibrahimu, koko ni wowe wagize utya imana zacu"
  21,63,"Aravuga ati \"Ahubwo byakozwe n’iki (kigirwamana) kinini muri byo! Ngaho nimubibaze niba bishobora kuvuga"
  21,64,"Nuko barigaya ubwabo, maze barabwirana bati \"Mu by’ukuri, ni mwe nkozi z’ibibi"
  21,65,"Nuko bubika imitwe (ariko banga kuva ku izima nyuma yo kumenya ukuri, baravuga) bati \"(Wowe Ibrahimu, ni gute udusaba kuzivugisha kandi) usanzwe uzi neza ko izi (mana zacu) zitavuga"
  21,66,"(Ibrahimu) aravuga ati \"Nonese ni gute musenga ibitari Allah; bitagira icyo bibamarira cyangwa ngo bigire icyo bibatwara"
  21,67,Ni igisebo kuri mwe no ku byo musenga bitari Allah. Ese nta bwenge mugira
  21,68,"Baravuga bati \"Nimumutwike (Ibrahimu) maze murengere imana zanyu, niba mushobora kugira icyo mukora"
  21,69,"Nuko twe (Allah) turavuga tuti \"Yewe muriro! Ba ubukonje n’amahoro kuri Ibrahimu"
  21,70,"Bashatse kumugirira nabi, (tuburizamo umugambi wabo mubisha) maze baba aribo bahinduka abanyagihombo"
  21,71,Nuko tumurokorana na Lutwi (Loti) tubajyanamu gihugu (cya Shami79) twashyiriyemo ibiremwa byose imigisha
  21,72,"Maze (Ibrahimu) tumuha impano (yo kubyara) Isihaqa (Isaka) tunamwongererahoYakubu (Yakobo, umwuzukuru we). Kandi bombi twabagize intungane"